Sentencas: The performances of solid oxide fuel cells with proton conductors BaCe0.7In0.3-xYxO3-delta (BCIY, x = 0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) as electrolytes were investigated in this work.
Titulo: Performance of solid oxide fuel cells based on proton-conducting BaCe0.7In0.3-xYxO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The cell based on BaCe0.7In0.2Y0.1O3-delta electrolyte showed maximum power outputs of 0.114, 0.204 and 0.269 wcm(-2) at 600, 650 and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Performance of solid oxide fuel cells based on proton-conducting BaCe0.7In0.3-xYxO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: After operating at a constant cell voltage output of 0.5V for 40h, no obvious degradation in performance was observed for the cells based on BaCe0.7In0.3O3-delta and BaCe0.7In0.2Y0.1O3-delta electrolytes.
Titulo: Performance of solid oxide fuel cells based on proton-conducting BaCe0.7In0.3-xYxO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: However, although relatively lower resistances and higher initial power outputs were found for cells based on BaCe0.7In0.1Y0.2O3-delta and BaCe0.7Y0.3O3-delta electrolytes, rapid cell performance degradations were observed for these two cells.
Titulo: Performance of solid oxide fuel cells based on proton-conducting BaCe0.7In0.3-xYxO3-δ electrolyte

Sentencas: The stability under cell operating conditions remained a challenge for cells using BaCe0.7In0.1Y0.2O3-delta and BaCe0.7Y0.3O3-delta electrolytes.
Titulo: Performance of solid oxide fuel cells based on proton-conducting BaCe0.7In0.3-xYxO3-δ electrolyte
